Great beach! Lovely sand and gentle surf. Highly recommended
Mar 2020
I've just returned from a motorcycle trip which ended at the beach in Da Nang and WOW, what a lovely beach! With the current virus scare, I found the beach almost empty, which is incredible!
I didn't see any evidence of litter, in fact its one of the cleanest beaches I've visited for many years.
I did try surfing, but the waves were a little too small on that day.
I'd have no hesitation in visiting this lovely beach again!
